name: CrackEDpad Tez Edition
description:
How did this happen? 

My neighbor ( the OG, crack dealer ) Pitt cracked my iPad Pro up. The owner refused to take responsibility because he was going to prison less than 3 weeks. I didn't argue too much because I didn't want trouble focused on me. That man has connections out the ass and could get my place mopped up if he wanted to. Despite the cracks I still used it to make art for as long as I could (1.5 month). The Matte screen protector was the only thing holding it together so it bought me some time. Unfortunately now its no longer usable for my Artistic endeavors. I really need to get it repaired or replaced so I can function at my highest capacity. 

All proceeds from this piece and my art will go towards repairing the biggest investment I've ever made in my art.
